high_descs: Turn and go to the coffee maker that is on the counter.
Pick up the white coffee mug that is on the coffee maker.
With the mug in hand turn and go to the microwave.
Place the mug in the microwave to the left of the egg.  Shut the door and start it.  When finished open the door and grab the coffee mug.
With the coffee mug in hand turn and go to the coffee maker.
Place the mug on the coffee maker on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Warm up coffee mug in microwave to place on coffee maker.

high_descs: Take the mug from the coffeemaker
Put the mug back in the coffeemaker
anns.task_desc: Heat a mug and place it back

high_descs: Turn right and take three steps, then turn right and take four steps, then turn right and walk to the counter.
Pick up the white coffee cup that is on the counter.
Turn to the left and walk across the room, then turn right to face the stove then look up.
Put the cup in the microwave then turn the microwave on for three seconds, then take the cup out of the microwave.
Look down and turn to the right then walk across the room, then turn left to face the counter.
Place the coffee mug on the coffee maker.
